body_html:
Hello , i am using tensorflow in windows. I tried every thing still i am getting no module name tensorflow
I tried following ways
C:> conda create -n tensorflow python=3.5
C:> activate tensorflow
pip install --ignore-installed --upgrade https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/windows/cpu/tensorflow-1.2.0-cp35-cp35m-win_amd64.whl

Still i am getting two errors
1 -tensorflow-1.2.0-cp35-cp35m-win_amd64.whl is not a supported wheel on this platform.
2- No module name tensorflow

body:
Hello , i am using tensorflow in windows. I tried every thing still i am getting no module name tensorflow
I tried following ways
C:> conda create -n tensorflow python=3.5 
C:> activate tensorflow
pip install --ignore-installed --upgrade https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/windows/cpu/tensorflow-1.2.0-cp35-cp35m-win_amd64.whl 

Still i am getting two errors
1 -tensorflow-1.2.0-cp35-cp35m-win_amd64.whl is not a supported wheel on this platform.
2- No module name tensorflow
